---
title: Shawarma-Spiced Chickpea & Bulgur Wraps with Greek Salad & Creamy Feta Dill Sauce
description: There are so many reasons why we love a hearty wrap… but the main one? We get to enjoy our favorite veggies, proteins, cheeses, and sauces, all at the same time. This Greek inspired, veggie-centric version stars one of our favorite ancient grains—chewy, nutty bulgur—then adds Shawarma-spiced and roasted chickpeas, a refreshing tomato-cucumber salad, creamy red pepper hummus, and salty feta cheese. On the side, there’s a tangy vinaigrette for drizzling or dipping each bite.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/shawarma-spiced-chickpea-bulgur-wraps-f086af02.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/shawarma-spiced-chickpea-bulgur-wraps-603662dffbc06f5a6600bb98-dccf7059.pdf
